project_descr:
Women in selected areas exercise their electoral rights and participate in voting 
Women and men actively promote peaceful elections 
Women are empowered to run as candidates during local elections

outputs.output_descr: The project aims at increasing women’s participation, including from minorities and youth groups, at elections, both as candidates and peaceful voters, in priority geographic areas under currently ongoing PRF projects.

project_title: women as peaceful voters & women as candidates
